#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Lakhani und Wolfs <a href=\"http://ocw.mit.edu/courses/sloan-school-of-"
#~ "management/15-352-managing-innovation-emerging-trends-spring-2005/"
#~ "readings/lakhaniwolf.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" title=\"Why Hackers Do What "
